[normal]We wish the BBC well and are sure that many would be reassured were the meretricious
[normal] 
[normal]to disappear along with 
[normal]the portrayal of 
[normal]extremes of evil.  The world and this country are
[normal] moving into a very challenging time.  People need to be helped to be serious and responsible at the expense of sensationalism.  The BBC's great value and past international reputation needs the Trust's help for this to be continued and, where damaged, res
[normal]tored. 
